-
vlans
show vlan
vlan 1 is defalut vlan

Static - dynamic -


-
 untagged
mode access (Untagged) - trunk (tagged) - dynamic tecih etme

access -> The port belongs to only one VLAN.
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10
trunk  -> The port carries multiple VLANs using tags (802.1Q).
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20,30
-

conf t 
vlan 10
name BT 
vlan 20
name IK 
end

conf t 
int gi0/2
switchport mode access -> this step is for incrase security
switchport access vlan 10
no sh

