Spaning Tree
conf t 
spaning-tree
spaning-tree mode ?
use Multible (mstp) or what u can use if your device is not support mstp
spanning-tree priority 0 (saldırıları azaltmak için)
spaning-tree pathcost method 
spaning-tree 

if client connect to port
int gi 0/6
spaning-tree portfast
spaning-tree bpduguard enable
